009

011     PaymentProjection<PaymentInfoProjection<PARENT, ROOT>, ROOT> projection = new PaymentProjection<>(this, getRoot());

014  }
015
016  public ReferenceProjection<PaymentInfoProjection<PARENT, ROOT>, ROOT> paymentRefs() {
017     ReferenceProjection<PaymentInfoProjection<PARENT, ROOT>, ROOT> projection = new ReferenceProjection<>(this, getRoot());

020  }
